                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    VIEWING YOUR ALERT RESULTS
                                </Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                The ATM ALERT application calculates each custom alert every five minutes.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                Results are dynamically displayed within each Alert
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" />

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    BEGIN CALCULATIONS:
                                </Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                Calculations begin, after selecting the '
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="PaleGreen">
                                    START
                                </Run>
                                ' button on your ATM Alert and continue every five minutes until stopped.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="RED">
                                    STOP
                                </Run>
                                a calculation by selecting the red Time Area '
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="Red">
                                    NEXT: 4:30
                                </Run>
                                ' where 4 is minutes and 30 is seconds.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" />

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    COMPLETED CALCULATIONS:
                                </Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                Once the calculation has completed, a white triangle '
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="8" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="White">
                                    &#x25B6;
                                </Run>
                                ' appears on the left side of the Alert Title Bar.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Table CellSpacing="0">
