                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    ALERT NOTIFICATION:
                                </Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                New or removed results cause the '
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="RED">
                                    ALERTS
                                </Run>
                                ' button to blink red.  Also, new results have a
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="RED">
                                    Red Diamond &#x2666;
                                </Run>
                                next to their Symbol.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                To close the Alert notifications, either select the ALERTS button at the top of the application or Open the Alert and select a Symbol.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" />

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    VIEW RESULTS:
                                </Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                Results - that have met your formula condition - are displayed as Symbols. Results are shown in 5 columns categorized by the shortest time frame in your condition formula.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                Bullish symbols appear on the left side of the results and bearish on the right side.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                The ATM Alert calculator samples your condition every five minutes.  If your formula’s shortest time frame is longer than five minutes,
                                a ‘TRUE’ reading could occur before the close of the shortest time frame. Should this occur, a
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    white strike &#x23AF;
                                </Run>
                                appears over the symbol.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                Once the bar of the shortest time frame in your condition closes, and the condition is confirmed true, it remains true.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" />

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    VIEW RESULTS ON CHARTS:
                                </Run>
                            </Paragraph>


                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                Selecting a Symbol, will open three charts with the shortest time frame in your formula represented in the bottom chart.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                A vertical blue line '
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="DodgerBlue">
                                    &#x2502;
                                </Run>
                                ' appears on the bottom chart and represents the time bar that met your condition.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11">
                                To
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    CLOSE
                                </Run>
                                the charts and return to the ATM Alerts display, select the
                                <Run FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#ff8c00">
                                    ' X '
                                </Run>
                                located at the top left of any of the three charts.
                            </Paragraph>

